@Node Patches "SystemPrefs: D. Patches"

  You can change the following parameters using "PatchEditor"
(available from my support mailbox):

Localization            Turns localization on or off. If off, System
                        Prefs uses the built-in language (English)
                        only. Default: on

Process name            Name of the program (default "SystemPrefs")

  Note that you are not allowed to distribute a program that has been
modified by PatchEditor.

@EndNode
